title: Full Stack Developer
job_overview:
We are seeking a Full Stack Developer skilled with AI assisted code to join our innovative team. In this role, you will leverage AI-powered tools to design, develop, and optimize high-quality software solutions. Responsibilities include writing clean, efficient code, collaborating with cross-functional teams, and integrating AI assistance to enhance productivity and problem-solving.

Key Requirements:

Node Js
Cursor
React
Supa base
React
Tailwinds
Nex js
Vercel

Experience with AI tools (e.g., GitHub Copilot, ChatGPT, v0, or similar)
Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail
Ability to adapt to evolving technologies and workflows
Join us to shape the future of software development with cutting-edge AI technology!
